These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Food: artichoke, pomegranate
City: paris, london
1. City:paris is in an even position##4
2. City:london == Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | pomegranate | artichoke |
| City     | london    | paris   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Cigar: game, baccarat
Hobby: filmmaking, cooking
1. Hobby:filmmaking is in an odd position##4
2. Cigar:baccarat is on the left of Cigar:game##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Cigar   | baccarat | game        |
| Hobby      | filmmaking  | cooking |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Game: bridge, domino
Transport: tram, van
1. Transport:tram is in an odd position##4
2. Game:domino is on the left of Game:bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Game   | domino    | bridge |
| Transport   | tram | van |

